- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences) is another possible category as the paper analyzes social interactions between individuals. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper generalizes existing notions of intra-community density and inter-community density, which are related to graph and network concepts. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may use machine learning techniques for analyzing the link stream data.
